column5: I decided to put a couple of trail cameras up at the cottage/home in minden, there is lots of wildlife around which makes it fun up there. also included a couple of pictures from the camera. Just thought I would share with everyone
Some great pictures there, thanks for putting them up.
Hahaha, first thought that was a fake owl sitting on top of the camera.
Wooow, you do not have to go far hunting
LOL My pop has like 20-30 deer he feeds during the winter. Go there for hunting season,Not a one taken. LOL
